# Reset Root/Admin Password

**How to reset root password?**

- Login to client portal from https://portal.serverpoint.com/cgi-bin/gen4cp/engine/login.cgi
- Click "Manage your Vms" 
- Click "Settings of the VM" and click "Actions"
- Click "Set New Password". A new random password will be emailed to you once the password is reset. This action will reboot your VM.
- Click "Reset"
